      "text": "Phase 1 вҶ’ Global CSS\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 2 вҶ’ Common Components\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 3 вҶ’ Individual Pages\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 4 вҶ’ Responsive Design\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 5 вҶ’ Animations\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 6 вҶ’ Theme & Dark Mode\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 7 вҶ’ Optimization",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Phase 1 вҶ’ Global CSS\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 2 вҶ’ Common Components\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 3 вҶ’ Individual Pages\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 4 вҶ’ Responsive Design\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 5 вҶ’ Animations\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 6 вҶ’ Theme & Dark Mode\n\nвҶ“\n\nPhase 7 вҶ’ Optimization",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
