      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "css/\n\nв”Ӯ\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ style.css              (Global Styles)\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ variables.css          (Colors & Fonts)\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ reset.css              (Reset Browser CSS)\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ components.css         (Buttons, Cards, Forms)\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ navbar.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ sidebar.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ footer.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ dashboard.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ login.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ profile.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ companies.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ roadmap.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ certificates.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ settings.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ admin.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ responsive.css\n\nв””в”Җв”Җ animations.css",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "css/\n\nв”Ӯ\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ style.css              (Global Styles)\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ variables.css          (Colors & Fonts)\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ reset.css              (Reset Browser CSS)\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ components.css         (Buttons, Cards, Forms)\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ navbar.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ sidebar.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ footer.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ dashboard.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ login.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ profile.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ companies.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ roadmap.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ certificates.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ settings.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ admin.css\n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ responsive.css\n\nв””в”Җв”Җ animations.css",
